        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14593576/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14593576/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/54532313/" class=" " title="未央">未央</a>
                (应无所住而生其心)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="14593576">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">凡所有相，皆是虚妄。若见诸相非相，即见如来。佛说世间万物皆是化相，此心若不动，万物即不动。缘起缘灭，缘生已空。

</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-09-21 12:54</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                凡所有相，皆是虚妄。若见诸相非相，即见如来。佛说世间万物皆是化相，此心若不动，万物即不动。缘起缘灭，缘生已空。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







